import CoffeeListStyle from '../Style/CoffeeList.module.css' import { Link } from 'react-router-dom' import Pic1 from '../Pic/CoffeeListPic/CinnamonAndCocoa.png' import Pic2 from '../Pic/CoffeeListPic/Coco&VanillaCream.png' import Pic3 from '../Pic/CoffeeListPic/BurstingBlueberry.png' import Pic4 from '../Pic/CoffeeListPic/DalgonaMacha.png' import Pic5 from '../Pic/CoffeeListPic/DrizzledWithCaramel.png' import Pic6 from '../Pic/CoffeeListPic/WhippedChocolate.png' const CoffeeList = () => { const CoffeeMap = [ {url:Pic1,price:'$99.00',name:'Cinnamon And Cocoa'}, {url:Pic2,price:'$199.00',name:'Coco & Vanilla Cream'}, {url:Pic3,price:'$120.00',name:'Bursting Blueberry'}, {url:Pic4,price:'$150.00',name:'Dalgona Macha'}, {url:Pic5,price:'$199.00',name:'Drizzled With Caramel'}, {url:Pic6,price:'$99.00',name:'Whipped Chocolate'}, ] return (
{CoffeeMap.map(item =>{ return(
{item.price}
{item.name}
) })}
) } export default CoffeeList
